OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Ffading during the evening, with clear
OL,7,Fskies developing for a time. However,
OL,8,Ffurther showers will arrive across the
OL,9,Fregion during the overnight period,
OL,10,Fthese heavy and blustery later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,13,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,14,Flocally heavy with hail and thunder.
OL,15,FFeeling rather cold with temperatures
OL,16,Fbelow normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
