OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FFurther heavy showers likely on
OL,7,FThursday and perhaps Friday, which
OL,8,Falso carry a risk of thunder. Some
OL,9,Fsunny spells in the mix too. Drier and
OL,10,Fbrighter on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
